	sem_ch2.adb: Minor reformatting

	* atree.ads, elists.ads, lib.ads, namet.ads, nlists.ads, repinfo.ads,
	sinput.ads, stringt.ads, uintp.ads, urealp.ads: Minor clarification to
	comments for Tree_Read and Tree_Write.

