	* Make-lang.in: Makefile automatically updated

2004-03-31  Richard Kenner  <kenner@vlsi1.ultra.nyu.edu>

	* decl.c (gnat_to_gnu_entity, make_type_from_size):
	Use TYPE_UNSIGNED, not TREE_UNSIGNED.
